parts.text: I will generate a professional marketing photograph. The image will feature a young Korean man in his thirties, dressed in a casual business outfit. He will be seated at a sleek, modern minimalist desk made of light wood or white material. On the desk, a closed laptop and a smartphone will be visible. The man's attention will be directed towards the smartphone screen, and his facial expression will convey thoughtfulness. The background will be a clean, white office space with soft, diffused natural light coming from the side. The overall mood will be warm and professional, and the image will be of high quality and photorealistic.
